---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — CleverWrite" description="CleverWrite privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your data." canonical="/privacy/">
  <main class="container section-block" style="padding-top:var(--space-4);padding-bottom:var(--space-5);max-width:800px">
    <h1 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-3)">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div style="font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--text-body);line-height:1.8">
      <p style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2)"><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 2026</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:var(--text-base);margin:var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-1)">1. Data Collection</h2>
      <p>We collect minimal data required to operate the service. Content you submit for processing is transmitted to our AI provider and is not stored on our servers after processing.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:var(--text-base);margin:var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-1)">2. Analytics</h2>
      <p>We use Google Analytics (GA4) to understand usage patterns. This includes anonymized page views and session data. No personal content is sent to analytics.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:var(--text-base);margin:var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-1)">3. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use minimal cookies: a theme preference cookie (localStorage) and analytics cookies from Google. No tracking or advertising cookies are used.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:var(--text-base);margin:var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-1)">4. Data Security</h2>
      <p>All data transmission is encrypted via HTTPS. Processed content is not stored, logged, or shared with third parties beyond the AI inference provider.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:var(--text-base);margin:var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-1)">5. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:zl18672545321@gmail.com">zl18672545321@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
